== مخينه ==
جنرال بسم الله خان د ۲۰۱۰ کال راپدېخوا وروسته د حنيف اتمر ته استعفاڅخه د حامد کرزي په حکومت کې د کورنيو چارو وزير وټاکل شو . 
بسم الله خان محمدي د پخواني کمونسټ گوند پرچم څانگې غړی و چې بيا وروسته ېې د احمد شاه مسعود گوند شورای نظار ته ځان تسليم کړ او ورسره مل شو . دی هم د پنشېر دی او په خټه تاجېک دی . 

Bismillah Khan was previously the [[Chief of staff (military)|Chief of Staff]] of the [[Afghan National Army]], a post he has held since 2002.<ref>Davis, Anthony. [http://www.janes.com/news/defence/jdw/jdw080118_2_n.shtml Interview: General Bismillah Khan Mohammadi, Chief of General Staff, Afghan National Army.] ''Jane's Defence News.'' 18 January 2008.</ref>

Before the fall of the [[Taliban]] in 2001, Bismillah Khan was the [[United Islamic Front for the Salvation of Afghanistan|Northern Alliance]]'s Deputy Minister of Defence, under [[Ahmad Shah Massoud]] and later under [[Mohammed Fahim]]. After the fall of Kabul to the Northern Alliance, he was appointed commander of the 2000 man Kabul police force, and a member of the Kabul Security Commission. He is an ethnic [[Tājik people|Tajik]] from the [[Panjshir Valley]].

